{
  "stem": "1338.6",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I love it, because it has both a metropolitan flavor to it, as well as a-- as a sort of a quieter life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a little bit more-- New York gives me a headache.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And how did you meet your wife, and when?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was-- I worked at-- I went to IIT, which is the school on the south side called the Illinois Institute of Technology.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, I always went to IIT because I also got my undergraduate in Israel Institute of Technology.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you see any symbolism to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, so I went to IIT.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked in Admiral for one year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Admiral used to make television, one of the largest companies in television at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in '54, I was got offered a job as an instructor and a-- well, I was a graduate student, but as an instructor at IIT.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I worked there until '58, first as an instructor, and then as a research engineer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I moved to what's called Armour Research Foundation, which is the Illinois Technology Research Institute-- the IIT Research Institute today used to be called Armour Research Foundation in '58.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked there as a research engineer, and I got my doctorate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In '63, I got the degree, but I left school already with all the requirements in '58.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Judy came to work as a computer programmer in 1962.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a cafeteria, and we met.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 1963.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have three children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had them pretty fast after each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Judy was very young, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was very concerned about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I considered my concern about my children not getting married today, I call it my mother's revenge.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
